<section xml:id="section-strategies-for-solving-quadratic-equations">

    <title>Strategies for Solving Quadratic Equations</title>

    <introduction>
        <p>In this section, we will review how to solve quadratic equations using three different methods: The square root method, factoring and the quadratic formula.</p>

